  <summary date="2020-12-21T15:13:52Z" status="Introduced in House">Opportunity Starts At Home Act

This bill allows a new tax credit for contributions to a reserve fund for low-income housing supportive services. These services include health services, job training, financial counseling, and resident engagement services and are provided at no cost to tenants of a qualified low-income building.</summary>
